name: Copper Ore
description: The most malleable and common of the ores, the uses of copper are unending.

name: Tin Ore
description: More sophisticated than copper, but equally industrious and multi-faceted in its uses.

name: Iron Ore
description: An indomitable ore, known for its might, it is the foundation of Ardent City and Castle.

name: Silver Ore
description: This elite, lustrous ore can be transformed into a great many sought after metals.

name: Copper Ingot
description: The most malleable and common of the ores, the uses of copper ingots are unending.

name: Silver Ingot
description: These ingots, of an elite and lustrous ore, can transformed into a great many sought after metals.

name: Wildpaw Leather
description: This supple leather is especially popular among trend-setting aristocrats.

name: Wildpaw Pelt
description: Wildpaw pelts are known for their soft downy fur.

name: Wildpaw Handgrip
description: A component piece to a sword, bow, staff, or mace.
